  <brief_title>Effectiveness of the Vasodilator Test With Revatio, Made in Patients With Acute Pulmonary Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study About Effectiveness of the Vasodilator Test With Revatio, Made in Patients With Acute Pulmonary Hypertension, at Last Moderate and Secondary at Valve Disease(Corrected With a Normally Functioning Prosthesis).</official_title>
  <sponsors>
