  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients clinically stable, at least 1 year after the completion of successful valve
             surgery, with persistent pulmonary artery systolic pressure&gt; 50 mmHg,

          -  normal left ventricular function and no significant valvular disease in 2 separate
             Doppler ultrasound studies at least 1 month.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with other cardiac and noncardiac diseases will be excluded.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
